{"tid":1800628,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科大編委總編、演藝記者採訪時遭搜身　便衣警：係咪好驚啊　","createTime":"2019-12-28T04:19:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T04:23:23.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"aa014013087fc56fb6ef9185af05eabbac71d248","tid":1800628,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T04:19:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Background_JzvJs_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FBackground_JzvJs_1200x0.png&h=2dd87a70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n科技大學學生編輯委員會報道，其總編輯與演藝學院一名學生記者，昨晚（27日）在屯門 V City 及屯門西鐵站採訪期間，被一名便衣警員制服搜身，期間便衣警員曾質問科大總編「得返兩個人，係咪好驚啊」，又指演藝沒有傳理系，質疑演藝學生記者身份。<br />\n<br />\n科大報道指，該名便衣警員搜查總編錢包期間，質問他為何需要將現金分開兩格擺放，科大總編則指是因為窮困，「把現金分開擺放可以看起來比較多。」報道指：「便衣警員未知是否憐憫窮困的學生記者，與本報總編相對無言。」<br />\n<br />\n警員奪手機阻拍攝<br />\n<br />\n報道又提及，該名便衣警員自稱屯門區反黑組第一隊警員，但無出示委任證；科大總編欲以手機錄影搜身過程時，被警員奪去手機。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%A7%91%E5%A4%A7%E7%B7%A8%E5%A7%94%E7%B8%BD%E7%B7%A8-%E6%BC%94%E8%97%9D%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%8E%A1%E8%A8%AA%E6%99%82%E9%81%AD%E6%90%9C%E8%BA%AB-%E4%BE%BF%E8%A1%A3%E8%AD%A6-%E4%BF%82%E5%92%AA%E5%A5%BD%E9%A9%9A-%E5%A5%AA%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E9%98%BB%E6%8B%8D%E6%94%9D/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25B7%25A8%25E5%25A7%2594%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B7%25A8-%25E6%25BC%2594%25E8%2597%259D%25E8%25A8%2598%25E8%2580%2585%25E6%258E%25A1%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E6%2599%2582%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%2590%259C%25E8%25BA%25AB-%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E8%25A1%25A3%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%2592%25AA%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E9%25A9%259A-%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F%25E9%2598%25BB%25E6%258B%258D%25E6%2594%259D%2F&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPOojXYTbvVfDxiGm1goFu7E%3D&h=8df61a07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics